    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a seal on the target's body, into which its bearer can pour up to 5 Chakra, reducing their maximum Chakra by the same amount while the seal is present. The Chakra inside the seal cannot be sensed, but creatures who can See (Through) Chakra gain a +4 bonus when trying to Spot the bearer.<br><br>As a free action, the bearer can release up to three seals created by this technique, removing the penalty to their maximum Chakra and regaining the Chakra poured into the seal when it was created. Releasing more than 3 seals at once is a move action. Each seal requires a Ninjutsu check (DC 15 + Chakra contained in the seal) to be released successfully. Attempting to release one or more seals provokes attacks of opportunity.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first, third and fifth step allow the seal to hold 1 additional Chakra each.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
